<li>
<p>
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sesame_Street">Sesame Street</a>
and the rest of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Muppets">The
<b>Muppets’</b></a> franchise.
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Trek">The
<b>Star Trek</b> franchise</a> ( especially
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Star_Trek%3A_The_Next_Generation"><i>The
