essays</a> (some of which are somewhat outdated),
<a href="[% base_path %]humour/">my works of humour and fiction</a> (which are
arguably both more serious, and not as funny as my essays),
the posts on my <a href="[% base_path %]me/blogs/">blogs</a>,
<a href="http://twitter.com/shlomif">my <b>Twitter</b> feed</a>, and other
Internet
